@startuml
title ATM Control - Withdraw Funds

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForAmount
state VerifyingTransaction
state ReleasingCard

Idle : entry / Display Welcome
Idle --> WaitingForAmount : Card Inserted / Get Amount

WaitingForAmount --> VerifyingTransaction : Amount Entered / Validate Amount
VerifyingTransaction --> ReleasingCard : Transaction Approved / Release Card

WaitingForAmount --> Idle : Cancel / Eject
VerifyingTransaction --> Idle : Rejected / Eject
ReleasingCard --> [*] : Transaction Completed / End

@enduml
